  "title": "Physiotherapy Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p>- Assist physiotherapists during treatments</p>\n<p>- Guide patients through exercises</p>\n<p>- Prepare equipment and treatment rooms</p>\n<p>- Support basic admin &amp; patient service duties</p>\n<p>- Maintain clinic hygiene and cleanliness</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p>- Possess of Degree in Physiotherapy</p>\n<p>- Possess at least 1 year experience in similar role</p>\n<p>- Passion for helping people regain health and mobility</p>\n<p>- Physically fit and willing to assist in hands-on therapy</p>\n<p>- Friendly and good communication skills</p>\n<p>- Prior healthcare experience is a bonus</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Perks &amp; Benefits:</strong></p>\n<p>- Friendly &amp; supportive environment</p>\n<p>- Career development opportunities</p>\n<p>- Staff discounts</p>",
